[Challenge Mode Codes\Opponent 1 Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=These codes only work for Challenge Mode. These codes call allow you to play against all of the same opponent or even against no opponents if you wish to explore the levels. Even though the opponent selection has who you designate as your opponent(s), you still have to make the selections. If a stage can only allow for up to 7 opponents, then you will only be permitted to face 7 opponents.
Values -
00 - Blank
01 - Junkyard Dog
02 - Brimstone
03 - Outlaw
04 - Mr. Grimm
05 - Roadkill
06 - Crazy 8
07 - Spectre
08 - Darkside
09 - Shadow
0A - Yellow Jacket
0B - Axel
0C - Wart Hog
0D - Man Slaughter
0E - Sweet Tooth
0F - Minion
10 - Black Razer (War Hawk) - GLITCHY
patch=1,EE,00486960,extended,00000000

[Opponent 1 Modifier]
author=BigBossman
description=These codes work for both Story & Challenge Modes. The values are the same as the Player 1 Modifier except the following:
Values - 
0200 - Warhawk (under the center of the stage)
0220 - No Opponent (instant win if only one opponent selected)
patch=1,EE,10425A74,extended,00000000

